snippet.title: Vishal Gad Kolhapur वर दगडफेकीनंतर हिंसाचार,घरांसह वाहनांची तोडफोड, काय घडलं?|Vishalgad Encroachment
snippet.description:
🔴लॉ़ग इन करा: https://www.mumbaitak.in/

#VishalGadKolhapur #EknathShinde #DevendraFadnavis #KolhapurVishalGad 

कोल्हापूर जिल्ह्यातील विशाळगड किल्ल्यावरच्या अतिक्रमणाचा मुद्दा पुन्हा एकदा तापला आहे. विशाळगडाच्या पायथ्याशी राहणाऱ्या लोकांवर अज्ञात आरोपींनी जीवघेणा हल्ला केला आहे. दगडफेक करत घरांसह गाड्यांची तोडफोड करण्यात आलीय, त्यानंतर आता कोल्हापूर पोलिसांनी तातडीने घटनास्थळी धाव घेतली असून परिसरात जमावबंदी लागू करण्यात आली आहे. #MHT005
---------

https://newstak.app.link/fataak

Website: https://www.mobiletak.in/mumbaitak

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/mumbaitak
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mumbaitak
Twitter: https://twitter.com/mumbai_tak

इंडिया टुडेच्या मुंबई तक या मराठी युट्यूब चॅनलवर आपलं स्वागत. इंडिया टुडे ग्रुपचे मॅगझिन, इंडिया टुडे टीव्ही आणि आज तक हे लोकप्रिय न्यूज चॅनल आपल्याला माहितीच आहे. त्यानंतर आता खास मराठी प्रेक्षकांसाठी आपण भारतीय प्रादेशिक भाषेतलं पहिलं मराठी चॅनल घेऊन आलोय. महाराष्ट्रासह राष्ट्रीय आणि आंतरराष्ट्रीयस्तरावरील महत्वाच्या बातम्या आणि घडामोडी आपल्याला अगदी सोप्या शब्दांत समजावण्याचा आमचा प्रयत्न असणार आहे.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4136 -  Dr. Hathi Ne Roki Popatlal ki Sagai?! I Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

Produced By: Neela Asit Modi, Asit Kumarr Modi 
Special Thanks: Mahesh Vakil, Indu Tarak Mehta
Set Design: Jayant Deshmukh

snippet.title: 100kg JAVA FRUIT | SWEET FRUIT JAM Recipe Cooking in Village | NAVAL PAZHAM | Black Plum Jamun Fruit
snippet.description:
Jamun Fruit is one of the favorite fruits available in south Indian and Indonesian villages. Today, we are making a sweet fruit jam recipe using this fruit. We call this fruit Naaval Pazham. Some other people call this fruit a Black plum or Java fruit.

We cook jam with jamun fruit pulp and palm jaggery. We enjoy the jam with the bread.

The taste is yummy!

snippet.title: Every South Indian Mass Movie Ever | Take A Break
snippet.description:
Prepare for a hilarious cinematic journey with our latest comedy sketch, "Every South Indian Mass Movie Ever"! 🎬🤣
In this uproarious video, we take you behind the scenes to reveal the formulaic brilliance that goes into making a quintessential South Indian mass movie. From the larger-than-life hero to the gravity-defying action sequences, no trope is left untouched in this side-splitting tribute to the world of South Indian cinema.
#SouthIndianCinema #ComedySketch #YouTubeSketch

Produced By - Monica Prabhudesai
Producer - Pratik Thakur
Creative Producer- Ravindra Sarowar

Script - Shreyas Koli
Direction - Shreyas Chougule
Associate Director- Sayali Sonule
AD - Sahil Parab

Production Design - Shashank Kalekar
Costume - Arru Jain
Production- Pavan Tekale
Production Asst.- Gajanan Lokhande
Spot - Navnath, Nilesh

Makeup- Shahin Baig
DOP - Suraj Kale & Akshay Jadhav
Camera Assistant - Hitan Dhaktode

Editor - Shubham Ghatkar
Post Production Supervisor & VFX - Hemant Vansh
Music - Prajwal Yadav, Manoj More
Mix & Master - Prajwal Yadav
DI - Mayur Satpute
Thumbnail - Anuj Shinde

Sound- Samir Sheikh & Manoj More
BTS- Malhari Shinde, Om Kanse

Jaan Nisar Episode 32 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 14th July 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

Welcome to an epic challenge series hosted by @CrazyXYZ  🚀
In this video, we bring you five thrilling challenges featuring educators from Unacademy's newest channels. Each challenge winner gets a mystery box worth up to ₹1 lakh! 🎁

Feel the excitement as our educators face off in intense bowling matches, zoom through go-karting races, and aim for victory in shooting competitions. Watch the strength hammer challenge push their limits and the mountain climbing contest reach new heights of exhilaration. From nervous anticipation to triumphant celebrations, every moment is packed with emotions and camaraderie. The video kicks off with introductions and a high-energy start, followed by each challenge that keeps you on the edge of your seat, and concludes with the crowning of the winners and the grand reveal of giveaways for the viewers.

Teams and Challenges:

1. 9th & 10th Foundation by Unacademy - Bowling (01:52)
➡️ Harsh Singhal Sir (Maths)

➡️ Divya Chandwani Ma’am (English)
➡️ Omhari Jadhav Sir (Chemistry)

2. Unacademy Avengers for Class 6th to 8th - Shooting  (10:19)
➡️ Asmita Singh Ma'am (English)
➡️ Supriya Ma’am (Social Science)
➡️ Ayush Shishodia Sir (Maths)

3. 10th Titans vs 9th Knights by Unacademy - Go-karting  (19:46)
➡️ Tapur Omar Ma’am (Chemistry)
➡️ Nikita Singh Ma’am (English)
➡️ Shweta Thakur Ma’am (Social Science)
➡️ Abhinay Rai Sir (Maths)
➡️ Alok Choubey Sir (Physics)
➡️ Shivangi Chauhan Ma'am (Biology)

4. NEET Phoenix by Unacademy - Mr. Hammer (26:13)
Featuring: Akansha Karnwal Ma’am (Top Chemistry Educator)
➡️ Tulika Jha Ma’am(Biology)
➡️ Sonali Malik Ma’am (Chemistry)
➡️ Preeti Diwakar Ma’am (Physics)

5. JEEfinity by Unacademy - Mountain Climbing (31:24)
Featuring: Arvind Kalia Sir #MeraBhai
➡️ Gaurav Singh Sir (Chemistry)
➡️ Sharad Bajpai Sir (Physics)
➡️ Prakhar Tripathi Sir (Maths)

Don't miss the fun and excitement! Make sure to watch, subscribe, and comment to win big! 🏆

snippet.title: 5th T20 | Hindi | Highlights | India Tour Of Zimbabwe | 14th July 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv
 
Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3OVl9LM

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-india-tour-of-zimbabwe-2024-1700000981

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

India and Zimbabwe faced each other in the 5th T20 at Harare Sports Club. India batted first and posted 167 runs at the end of their 20 overs. Sanju Samson was the star with the bat thanks to a vital 58 runs. Zimbabwe later crumbled against the Indian bowling attack and became all out for just 125 runs. India won by 42 runs in the end and sealed the series 4 - 1.

India and Zimbabwe faced each other in the 4th T20 at Harare Sports Club. India won the toss and elected to bowl first. India later chased down the target in just 15.2 overs and sealed a ten-wicket win thanks to Jaiswal and Gill.

Teens and adults can now level up their own creative engineering skills and build their very own robot alongside me: http://crunchlabs.com/puzzle

If anyone had a shot at beating Jigsaw it would've been Tammy! Check her out:

hi.description:

टीन्स और एडल्ट्स अब अपने स्वयं के क्रिएटिव इंजीनियरिंग स्किल को बढ़ा सकते हैं और मेरे साथ अपना स्वयं का रोबोट बना सकते हैं: https://crunchlabs.com/puzzle

अगर किसी के पास जिगसॉ को हराने का मौका होता तो वह टैमी होती! उसे देखें: https://www.instagram.com/tammymcleodpuzzler/

जिगसॉ पजल सॉल्व करने वाला रोबोट कैसे काम करता है, इसकी जानकारी यहाँ देखें: https://crunchlabs.com/puzzletech

एविड सीएनसी को विशेष धन्यवाद: https://www.avidcnc.com/

این ۲۰۰ برابر سریع‌تر از انسان است به شرطی که ۳ سالی را که برای ساخت آن صرف شده است را در نظر نگیرید. Hack Pack یک جعبه اشتراک ربات DIY است که برای نوجوانان و بزرگسالان بدون نیاز به تجربه کدنویسی مناسب است! یک جعبه رایگان دریافت کنید در: http://crunchlabs.com/puzzle

pa.title: ਇਹ ਪਜ਼ਲ ਰੋਬੋਟ ਮਨੁੱਖ ਤੋਂ 200 ਗੁਣਾ ਤੇਜ਼ ਹੈ
pa.description:
ਇਹ 200 ਗੁਣਾ ਤੇਜ਼ ਹੈ ਜੇਕਰ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਇਸਨੂੰ ਬਣਾਉਣ ਵਿੱਚ ਲੱਗੇ 3 ਸਾਲ ਨਹੀਂ ਸ਼ਾਮਲ ਕਰਦੇ। ਹੈਕ ਪੈਕ ਇੱਕ DIY ਰੋਬੋਟ ਸਬਸਕ੍ਰਿਪਸ਼ਨ ਬਾਕਸ ਹੈ ਜੋ ਕਿਸੇ ਵੀ ਕੋਡਿੰਗ ਤਜਰਬੇ ਦੀ ਲੋੜ ਨਹੀਂ ਹੈ! ਇੱਕ ਮੁਫ਼ਤ ਬਾਕਸ ਪ੍ਰਾਪਤ ਕਰੋ: http://crunchlabs.com/puzzle

ਨੌਜਵਾਨ ਅਤੇ ਬਾਲਗ ਹੁਣ ਆਪਣੀਆਂ ਰਚਨਾਤਮਕ ਇੰਜੀਨੀਅਰਿੰਗ ਦੇ ਕੌਸ਼ਲ ਨੂੰ ਵਧਾ ਸਕਦੇ ਹਨ ਅਤੇ ਮੇਰੇ ਨਾਲ ਮਿਲ ਕੇ ਆਪਣਾ ਰੋਬੋਟ ਬਣਾ ਸਕਦੇ ਹਨ: http://crunchlabs.com/puzzle

ਜੇ ਕਿਸੇ ਨੇ Jigsaw ਨੂੰ ਹਰਾਉਣ ਦਾ ਮੌਕਾ ਮਿਲਿਆ ਹੋਵੇਗਾ, ਤਾਂ ਉਹ Tammy ਸੀ! ਉਸਨੂੰ ਦੇਖੋ: https://www.instagram.com/tammymcleodpuzzler/

Avid CNC ਦਾ ਵਿਸ਼ੇਸ਼ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ: https://www.avidcnc.com/

ਜਾਨੋ ਕਿ Jigsaw ਰੋਬੋਟ ਕਿਵੇਂ ਕੰਮ ਕਰਦਾ ਹੈ, ਇਹਨਾਂ ਨਰਡੀ ਵਿਸ਼ੇਸ਼ਤਾਵਾਂ ਨਾਲ: https://crunchlabs.com/puzzletech

ਵਿਡੀਓ ਵਿੱਚ ਕੁਝ ਸੰਗੀਤ ਪ੍ਰਦਾਨ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਇਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਲੋਕਾਂ ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ:

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4136 | 13 July 2024 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4136: Popatlal Gayab Hain
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal goes missing on his engagement day, and Inspector Pandey holds the Gokuldham members responsible for his disappearance. The entire community is in turmoil, asking themselves where Popatlal is and whether he will show up for his engagement.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4136 | 13 July 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1000282777

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4135: Popatlal's Engagement Ceremony
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal's engagement ceremony is coming up and everyone is eager to welcome his beautiful bride into the family. But will the big day go off without a hitch?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4135 | 12 July 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1000282689

snippet.title: சூறாவளி புயல் in our Garden | Steffi Vlog in Tamil
snippet.description:
Our garden has suffered some damage during the recent weather events. A lot of broken branches from nearby trees have damaged our small plants. Strong winds have also bent several trees and thrown debris all our our backyard. We have tried to salvage all we could and we are fixing things over the next few weeks.
#steffiulagam #steffigarden

Friends, hope you liked today's vlog and see you soon with more interesting videos. Also, I hope you will find some inspiration to grow some plants and home and spread the joy of gardening in the face of all challenges.

snippet.title: Eating The BEST BURGER For 24 Hours Challenge 🍔🔥
snippet.description:
Welcome to FoodieWe, your ultimate guide to finding the best burger in India! Join our passionate food explorers Onkar, Mukti, and Aditya as they embark on a mouth-watering journey across the country, visiting a wide variety of unique burger outlets. They're on a mission to taste, review, and rank the best burgers India has to offer, leaving no stone unturned.

In their quest, they'll be trying out burgers from popular spots like Burger Singh, Burger Club, and many more exciting and lesser-known burger joints. However, they won't be stopping at the most famous chains like McDonald's, Burger King, and KFC, as their burgers are already well-known and widely reviewed. Instead, FoodieWe focuses on discovering hidden gems and iconic local favorites that truly showcase the diversity and creativity of India's burger scene.

Subscribe to join Onkar, Mukti, and Aditya on their exciting food adventures, where you'll get honest reviews, behind-the-scenes looks at burger-making processes, and plenty of deliciousness. Whether you're a burger enthusiast or just love exploring new flavors, FoodieWe is your go-to channel for the ultimate burger experience in India!

Onkar ka Instagram -  https://www.instagram.com/onkarrandhawa/?hl=en

snippet.title: SAZA | King & MC Heam | Monopoly Moves | Official Music Video
snippet.description:
“SAZA'' arrives as the seventh single from KING’s upcoming “Monopoly Moves” album, and marks his debut collaboration with seasoned rapper/singer-songwriter MC Heam. Adorned by an infectious, yet soulful production effort courtesy Exult Yowl, KING and Heam pair up to double down on the enchanting allure of their melodic craftsmanship to deliver a monsoon-friendly groove as they confess their emotions to their love interest while laying down a smooth & memorable hook, while taking a leaf out of the New Delhi-based artist’s knack for creating bittersweet bops.

STREAM NOW : https://out-now.lnk.to/_SAZA

Song Name : SAZA
Artist : KING
Lyrics : KING, MC Heam
Music Producer : Exult Yowl
Composed by : KING, MC Heam
Additional Vocals : Priyanshi Srivastava
Mixed by : Hanish Taneja

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
